r:#991B1B;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;Why this matters&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size:10px;color:#7F1D1D;margin-top:4px;&quot;&gt;Auto-isolating the wrong host is worse than the attack.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
